    <div style="background-color:white;width:100%">
    	<h2 style="color:#3BD7F3;text-align:left">Loops</h2>
        <p style="color:black;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong>Definition:</strong>A loop is a sequence of code/instructions that are repeated until a certain condition is satisfied.</p>
        <p style="color:black;font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong>Analogy:</strong>One keeps brushing their hair until all the knots in a strand are gone. If with one brush the knot is still there, one brushes that same piece again until the knots are gone.</p>
